1
00:00:00,428 --> 00:00:08,528
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,703 --> 00:00:16,940
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,178 --> 00:00:19,169
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,183 --> 00:00:25,949
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,020 --> 00:00:29,387
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,591 --> 00:00:33,152
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,528 --> 00:00:36,895
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:36,965 --> 00:00:44,394
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,472 --> 00:00:53,608
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,681 --> 00:01:01,713
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:01,956 --> 00:01:08,794
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,863 --> 00:01:16,929
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,238 --> 00:01:25,703
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,780 --> 00:01:27,805
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:41,573 --> 00:01:42,335
Uh oh!

16
00:01:43,575 --> 00:01:44,269
Pakkun?

17
00:01:45,177 --> 00:01:46,007
Sakura?

18
00:01:51,683 --> 00:01:54,311
Why did you stop
all of a sudden?!

19
00:01:54,953 --> 00:01:59,686
The scents of Sasuke and the other two...
are quickly moving away!

20
00:02:00,425 --> 00:02:04,156
It smells like Sasuke is
chasing those two people...

21
00:02:05,097 --> 00:02:05,791
What?!

22
00:02:05,997 --> 00:02:06,895
Sasuke is?

23
00:02:07,399 --> 00:02:09,264
There are no other signs
of movement.

24
00:02:09,901 --> 00:02:10,890
But...

25
00:02:11,536 --> 00:02:15,404
Let's not just stand around.
Let's go after Sasuke right away!

26
00:02:16,041 --> 00:02:17,599
But... what?

27
00:02:18,243 --> 00:02:20,803
The people who are left are going
to fight each other.

28
00:02:23,081 --> 00:02:24,673
We'll end up taking a little longer way...

29
00:02:25,150 --> 00:02:26,674
but all there is for us to do
is to avoid it.

30
00:02:27,152 --> 00:02:31,486
Why?! If we do that, it'll only delay our
catching up to Sasuke.

31
00:02:31,790 --> 00:02:32,848
Let's just speed on through!

32
00:02:32,924 --> 00:02:34,687
What are you saying, Naruto?!

33
00:02:35,026 --> 00:02:37,586
We don't know what'll happen
in the battle zone!

34
00:02:38,363 --> 00:02:39,830
Even if we don't desire it,

35
00:02:39,898 --> 00:02:43,459
there's a possibility that
we'll be irrepressibly caught up in a battle.

36
00:02:43,702 --> 00:02:45,727
That doesn't have anything
to do with it!

37
00:02:45,971 --> 00:02:49,532
Kid! Our mission is to bring
Sasuke back.

38
00:02:50,108 --> 00:02:53,737
So the cardinal rule is to avoid battle
as much as possible until then!

39
00:02:53,945 --> 00:02:55,378
- Let's go!
- Got it!

40
00:02:56,815 --> 00:02:58,043
Fine!

41
00:03:14,166 --> 00:03:15,428
<i>Puppet Master Jutsu!</i>

42
00:04:01,079 --> 00:04:03,809
I'm from the Aburame Clan
of the Leaf Village...

43
00:04:04,482 --> 00:04:08,384
When we fight,
we never underestimate our opponent,

44
00:04:08,453 --> 00:04:09,818
no matter what puny insects
they may be.

45
00:04:10,088 --> 00:04:11,077
I'll advance with full force!

46
00:04:12,657 --> 00:04:13,555
Bring it!

47
00:04:36,047 --> 00:04:38,106
Put me down, Temari.

48
00:04:38,650 --> 00:04:40,140
Can you move, Gaara?

49
00:04:45,156 --> 00:04:45,884
Gaara!

50
00:04:51,663 --> 00:04:54,131
<i>Kankuro is delaying Uchiha now.</i>

51
00:04:54,933 --> 00:04:55,957
<i>We must use this opening...</i>

52
00:04:59,504 --> 00:05:01,529
<i>If we don't get a move on,</i>
<i>the operation will...</i>

53
00:05:02,841 --> 00:05:03,500
Huh?!

54
00:05:04,276 --> 00:05:06,778
Temari, go over there.

55
00:05:06,778 --> 00:05:07,472
What?

56
00:05:07,679 --> 00:05:11,843
Just beat it! You're in the way!

57
00:05:35,073 --> 00:05:41,205
<i>Astonishing Truth!</i>
<i>Gaara's Identity Emerges!</i>

58
00:06:10,475 --> 00:06:11,601
<i>Poison on the blade!</i>

59
00:06:24,723 --> 00:06:25,951
I won't let you get away!

60
00:06:42,774 --> 00:06:46,801
<i>That's... Sasuke Uchiha!</i>
<i>Did he get past Kankuro?!</i>

61
00:06:47,345 --> 00:06:49,643
<i>No... No matter how you look at it,</i>
<i>it's too soon.</i>

62
00:06:50,715 --> 00:06:52,444
<i>Did another assailant come?</i>

63
00:06:53,351 --> 00:06:56,149
I don't know what you Sand Ninja
are scheming...

64
00:06:56,855 --> 00:06:59,085
but <i>I'll</i> stop you!

65
00:07:01,292 --> 00:07:02,190
And...

66
00:07:08,633 --> 00:07:11,227
I'll ascertain your true identity!

67
00:07:15,807 --> 00:07:16,501
Gaara!

68
00:07:21,446 --> 00:07:22,413
<i>Don't tell me...!</i>

69
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:25,547
<i>Is he going to rouse that thing</i>
<i>in a place like this?!</i>

70
00:07:25,850 --> 00:07:28,717
<i>This is no joke...</i>
<i>It's out of my hands.</i>

71
00:07:29,821 --> 00:07:32,221
Stop, Gaara!
Have you forgotten the operation?!

72
00:07:32,690 --> 00:07:36,421
You who are strong...
You who are called Uchiha...

73
00:07:37,128 --> 00:07:38,595
You who have friends...

74
00:07:39,330 --> 00:07:40,991
You who have a purpose...

75
00:07:41,499 --> 00:07:45,299
You who are like... me!

76
00:07:47,705 --> 00:07:49,764
By killing you...

77
00:07:50,008 --> 00:07:54,911
I will exist in this world as
the one who destroyed all of that...

78
00:07:57,048 --> 00:07:59,312
I can truly experience "life."

79
00:08:02,153 --> 00:08:03,085
What is it?

80
00:08:03,955 --> 00:08:06,890
It's so obvious if you release
such a blood thirsty aura...

81
00:08:07,091 --> 00:08:08,718
Come on out.

82
00:08:15,166 --> 00:08:16,292
So it's you, eh...

83
00:08:17,702 --> 00:08:22,799
What's your purpose?
Why do you seek power?

84
00:08:29,113 --> 00:08:31,138
It's none of your business.

85
00:08:32,183 --> 00:08:34,777
Beat it!
You're a hindrance to my training.

86
00:08:47,465 --> 00:08:48,432
You...

87
00:08:50,268 --> 00:08:52,236
have the same eyes as I do.

88
00:08:53,371 --> 00:08:58,502
Eyes that seek power,
brimming with hate and murderous intent.

89
00:08:58,743 --> 00:09:00,108
You're like me.

90
00:09:00,845 --> 00:09:04,576
Don't forget... You're my...

91
00:09:06,518 --> 00:09:07,416
You're...

92
00:09:08,286 --> 00:09:09,344
my...

93
00:09:24,135 --> 00:09:28,504
You're... my...

94
00:09:31,142 --> 00:09:34,634
my prey!

95
00:09:39,584 --> 00:09:40,881
<i>It's started...!</i>

96
00:09:53,031 --> 00:09:53,861
A Substitution?!

97
00:09:57,669 --> 00:09:58,499
You're naive.

98
00:10:09,381 --> 00:10:10,405
All right!

99
00:10:21,393 --> 00:10:22,052
<i>Insects?!</i>

100
00:10:26,965 --> 00:10:28,694
To think you'd make
a clone out of insects and

101
00:10:28,767 --> 00:10:30,462
wrap around behind me...

102
00:10:30,669 --> 00:10:31,658
Not bad!

103
00:10:32,371 --> 00:10:35,738
Your reach encompasses from medium
to long distance and you use a puppet.

104
00:10:36,275 --> 00:10:38,038
I didn't think you would
do well in close combat.

105
00:10:38,443 --> 00:10:42,174
With that Puppet Master Jutsu
where you have to concentrate

106
00:10:42,247 --> 00:10:44,112
on the control of the puppet...

107
00:10:45,050 --> 00:10:47,780
the one casting the Jutsu is
prone to openings in defense.

108
00:10:49,087 --> 00:10:52,648
You're very aware of the weakness
of a puppet master!

109
00:10:53,058 --> 00:10:55,356
However, from here on,

110
00:10:55,427 --> 00:10:58,863
I'll show you the essence of
this Ninjutsu fighting style!

111
00:11:00,065 --> 00:11:03,865
The real terror of Crow...
my puppet of warfare!

112
00:11:13,979 --> 00:11:16,174
<i>This is Poison Smoke Bomb!</i>

113
00:11:26,625 --> 00:11:28,650
<i>Did I inhale...a little bit?</i>

114
00:11:29,494 --> 00:11:33,692
<i>I get it...</i>
<i>And the caster of the Jutsu hides, eh?</i>

115
00:11:56,455 --> 00:11:57,422
Listen, everyone...

116
00:11:58,156 --> 00:12:01,717
Even if enemy Shinobi appear,
don't panic.

117
00:12:01,793 --> 00:12:03,624
Go into the hidden room quickly.

118
00:12:06,932 --> 00:12:12,063
Your Jonin and Chunin Senseis
will protect you all with their lives!

119
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:29,316
Oh!

120
00:12:30,088 --> 00:12:31,282
Konohamaru...

121
00:12:32,157 --> 00:12:33,283
It'll be okay!

122
00:12:34,226 --> 00:12:35,625
Everyone's doing their best.

123
00:12:36,461 --> 00:12:38,486
They can drive away
the enemies right away.

124
00:12:49,474 --> 00:12:51,669
Cracks in the face rock
of the Hokage Lords...

125
00:12:52,411 --> 00:12:54,106
<i>How ominous...</i>

126
00:12:56,381 --> 00:12:57,313
<i>Grandpa...</i>

127
00:13:15,834 --> 00:13:19,065
<i>To have come this far...</i>
<i>To have come this far...!</i>

128
00:13:20,272 --> 00:13:27,269
<i>Do I already lack the power</i>
<i>to drag out his soul?</i>

129
00:13:28,647 --> 00:13:30,672
<i>With this feeble body...</i>

130
00:13:30,749 --> 00:13:33,843
<i>even though I'm prepared to die,</i>
<i>is it not enough...?!</i>

131
00:13:34,853 --> 00:13:40,120
<i>You probably could've killed me</i>
<i>if you'd been ten years younger.</i>

132
00:13:53,071 --> 00:13:58,008
Sarutobi! If you don't kill him now,
the village is doomed!

133
00:13:58,376 --> 00:13:59,968
Do you understand?!

134
00:14:00,912 --> 00:14:03,244
I... understand!

135
00:14:13,458 --> 00:14:16,859
Useless... old man...

136
00:14:39,718 --> 00:14:42,414
Now... Let me feel it!

137
00:14:44,422 --> 00:14:45,184
<i>That eye!</i>

138
00:14:48,293 --> 00:14:50,727
<i>That eye...from before!</i>

139
00:15:32,671 --> 00:15:36,732
<i>This doesn't look like it'll end</i>
<i>by the time you come for back up...</i>

140
00:15:37,609 --> 00:15:38,473
Shino...

141
00:15:45,116 --> 00:15:47,641
<i>It looks like the poison has</i>
<i>slowly started to circulate.</i>

142
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:50,181
<i>I'll finish this!</i>

143
00:16:03,635 --> 00:16:04,761
<i>Insects, again?!</i>

144
00:16:05,770 --> 00:16:08,238
<i>But he shouldn't be able to</i>
<i>move so much in that state...</i>

145
00:16:17,082 --> 00:16:18,982
<i>I'll make things easier for you...</i>

146
00:16:21,953 --> 00:16:23,079
<i>Hey! What's wrong?!</i>

147
00:16:27,425 --> 00:16:28,517
<i>What's happening...?</i>

148
00:16:31,963 --> 00:16:33,021
<i>Don't tell me...!</i>

149
00:16:33,798 --> 00:16:36,995
It's futile...
He can't move anymore...

150
00:16:38,103 --> 00:16:41,334
I had the beetles burrow
into every joint...

151
00:16:43,875 --> 00:16:46,639
<i>He stuffed beetles into its joints</i>
<i>so that the puppet can't move?</i>

152
00:16:47,679 --> 00:16:49,874
<i>That was his aim from the beginning!</i>

153
00:16:51,116 --> 00:16:53,584
<i>The beetles are passing through</i>
<i>the threads of my Chakra...</i>

154
00:16:54,552 --> 00:16:55,177
<i>Why...?</i>

155
00:16:56,588 --> 00:17:00,149
<i>That's it!</i>
<i>As I recall, their food is Chakra.</i>

156
00:17:05,864 --> 00:17:07,627
<i>At this rate,</i>
<i>my location will be found out!</i>

157
00:17:11,503 --> 00:17:14,336
<i>He cut the Chakra threads himself...?</i>

158
00:17:27,786 --> 00:17:28,878
<i>You got careless!</i>

159
00:17:29,554 --> 00:17:33,251
<i>Instantly reattaching the Chakra threads</i>
<i>that have once been cut</i>

160
00:17:33,325 --> 00:17:36,692
<i>is simple for a first rate puppet master.</i>

161
00:17:37,095 --> 00:17:37,789
<i>And...</i>

162
00:17:38,363 --> 00:17:41,161
<i>Crow is a puppet...</i>

163
00:17:41,633 --> 00:17:45,228
<i>that has a weapon in each</i>
<i>and every component of the body!</i>

164
00:17:47,572 --> 00:17:50,268
<i>It's a big mistake if you think</i>
<i>this has ended...</i>

165
00:17:51,109 --> 00:17:52,508
<i>by your stopping my movements!</i>

166
00:17:53,144 --> 00:17:55,908
<i>There's lots of poison</i>
<i>on the tip of the needle...</i>

167
00:17:56,848 --> 00:17:57,678
<i>Die!</i>

168
00:18:07,992 --> 00:18:08,720
<i>What?!</i>

169
00:18:19,170 --> 00:18:20,660
<i>Just like that, the insects...!</i>

170
00:18:21,706 --> 00:18:23,731
<i>The Chakra threads have been</i>
<i>bitten through!</i>

171
00:18:37,589 --> 00:18:39,147
What?! Why...?!

172
00:18:39,524 --> 00:18:42,322
Where did these insects
spring out from?!

173
00:18:43,595 --> 00:18:47,156
By beating away the bait insects
along the Chakra threads,

174
00:18:47,232 --> 00:18:48,324
you dropped your guard.

175
00:18:48,767 --> 00:18:53,670
You didn't notice...
the wriggling insects behind you.

176
00:18:56,574 --> 00:18:58,667
The insects were moving
the whole time...

177
00:18:59,711 --> 00:19:02,339
heading for your headband.

178
00:19:02,881 --> 00:19:04,508
W-What did you say?!

179
00:19:05,183 --> 00:19:06,480
The one blow earlier...

180
00:19:06,885 --> 00:19:12,016
I pretended to miss and
stuck one of those beetles on you.

181
00:19:17,228 --> 00:19:21,062
But how did you know where I was
with one such beetle?

182
00:19:22,133 --> 00:19:26,092
I... hate explaining the same thing twice.

183
00:19:29,607 --> 00:19:33,236
<i>Shino?</i>
<i>Why are you here?!</i>

184
00:19:36,648 --> 00:19:40,948
<i>I put a female beetle on you</i>
<i>before you left the arena!</i>

185
00:19:42,454 --> 00:19:44,684
<i>The females have almost no smell...</i>

186
00:19:46,357 --> 00:19:50,885
<i>Only a male can sniff out</i>
<i>the subtle smell of the female.</i>

187
00:19:51,963 --> 00:19:53,794
Then, this one beetle on my forehead...

188
00:19:55,033 --> 00:19:56,933
Right... It's a female.

189
00:20:07,345 --> 00:20:10,314
The poison has circulated
through my whole body, huh...

190
00:20:12,217 --> 00:20:14,515
<i>It looks like I won't be able</i>
<i>to go to back you up...</i>

191
00:20:15,153 --> 00:20:18,782
<i>I'm sorry, Sasuke Uchiha.</i>

192
00:20:26,531 --> 00:20:28,726
Is he a... monster?

193
00:20:33,771 --> 00:20:38,003
Are you scared of me, Sasuke Uchiha?!

194
00:20:42,747 --> 00:20:45,045
Of my existence?!

195
00:20:47,118 --> 00:20:51,612
Come out...
Sasuke Uchiha!

196
00:20:53,391 --> 00:20:55,951
You're... my...

197
00:20:56,494 --> 00:21:00,863
prey!

198
00:21:05,670 --> 00:21:15,739
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

199
00:21:16,180 --> 00:21:27,023
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

200
00:21:37,134 --> 00:21:42,766
<i>Yes, breathe in the air</i>
<i>Lift your face to the sky and jump</i>

201
00:21:42,840 --> 00:21:47,800
<i>If it rains, take a break</i>
<i>Go where the wind takes you</i>

202
00:21:48,179 --> 00:21:53,082
<i>So many regrets</i>
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>

203
00:21:53,150 --> 00:21:58,281
<i>Let's go carve the badges in our chest</i>
<i>Yes, it's Show Time, life begins now.</i>

204
00:21:58,356 --> 00:22:08,527
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

205
00:22:08,833 --> 00:22:19,266
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

206
00:22:19,343 --> 00:22:29,912
<i>Transform sadness into the wind</i>
<i>and continue to forge on</i>

207
00:22:29,987 --> 00:22:35,550
<i>Forge on strong</i>

208
00:22:48,639 --> 00:22:50,504
What a speed and strength!

209
00:22:51,409 --> 00:22:53,502
If I didn't use my Sharingan
to foresee his movement,

210
00:22:53,577 --> 00:22:55,101
I would have been in pieces!

211
00:22:56,080 --> 00:22:58,207
But a merely defensive battle
will do no good.

212
00:22:58,783 --> 00:22:59,807
What do I do?

213
00:22:59,984 --> 00:23:03,886
How should I stop him?
Do I need to use that?

214
00:23:04,522 --> 00:23:06,683
But Chidori may not...

215
00:23:08,092 --> 00:23:11,721
Next time: "Sasuke's Decision:
Pushed to the Edge!"
